{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_04_03",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、着替え終わりました～",
      "startTime": 3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 5.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "どうやろ？　ふふっ、嬉しいけど\nやっぱり少し照れますなぁ",
      "startTime": 10.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "てっきりウエディングドレスかと思っていたら\n白無垢か……さすが京都……",
      "startTime": 15.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 20
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、うち可愛いですか？\nなかなかいいんとちゃいます？",
      "startTime": 24.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんと、どっちが好みですか？",
      "startTime": 27.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……鈴村さん、もうすぐカメラが回るから",
      "startTime": 30.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、分かりました。うまいこと逃げたなぁ",
      "startTime": 36.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "さてみなさん、この結婚衣装の撮影サービスは\n今、若い女性の間で流行ってるそうです",
      "startTime": 45.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "SNSに動画を上げる方も多いらしいですよ～",
      "startTime": 49.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（普段のステージ衣装もいいけど）\n（鈴村さんは和服が映えるな……）",
      "startTime": 56.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "女の子同士での来店も歓迎してるみたいやし\n興味のある方はぜひ、お立ち寄り下さい～",
      "startTime": 63.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（トリエルのステージ衣装）\n（いつか和をコンセプトにしてもいいかもしれないな）",
      "startTime": 69.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみにみなさん、この衣装、どうです？\nほんまに可愛く着れてるやろか……不安です",
      "startTime": 76.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "せや、マネージャーさんはどう思います？\n感想お願いします",
      "startTime": 84.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　……ま、また俺なのか？\n……はい。とっても可愛いですよ、凄く似合ってます！",
      "startTime": 91.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、嬉しいなぁ。ありがとうございます～\nその言葉が聞きたかったんです",
      "startTime": 100.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "では、鈴村優の京都散策レポート、今回はここまでです\nみなさん、またお会いしましょ～",
      "startTime": 109.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 113.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……お疲れ様。凄く良かったよ。さすがだな",
      "startTime": 114.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 119.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、えらい疲れてはるなぁ\n花嫁衣装、似合ってるって言ってくれて嬉しかったです",
      "startTime": 123.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 128.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……あれは、言わせた、って言うんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 128.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　じゃあ似合ってへんていうこと？\nうち悲しいわぁ",
      "startTime": 136.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 138.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうやって、本番でも舞台裏でも\n俺をいじるのは、控え目にしてくれ……",
      "startTime": 140.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ごめんなさい。でもそれは、相手が\n{user}さんやったから……",
      "startTime": 148.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 150.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "俺が相手だったから……？　それってどういう……",
      "startTime": 150.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんやったら、ええリアクション\nしてくれる、って信じてたから振ったんよ",
      "startTime": 158.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……次からはお手柔らかにしてくれ",
      "startTime": 161.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 165.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "今日は本当に感謝してます",
      "startTime": 165.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 168.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "ふるさとの京都で、こんな綺麗な衣装\n着させていただきました",
      "startTime": 171.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "きっと父も母も喜んでくれますわぁ",
      "startTime": 173.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 177.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 182.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、せやせや。今の姿、写真撮って送ったろ\n{user}さん、ちょっと失礼します",
      "startTime": 182.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8533.333333299994,
          "startTime": 186
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……両親に送る写真なんだよな？\nどうして俺と一緒に撮るんだ？",
      "startTime": 190.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 192.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、お父さん、お母さん\nうち、ええ人見つかりました……っと",
      "startTime": 197.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 201.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "こらこらこら！　誤解されるからやめてくれ！",
      "startTime": 201.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 205.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
